    "description": "dnata India South Asia Partners is actively seeking a talented and motivated Hotel Manager to join our dynamic team in Visakhapatnam. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout dnata India South Asia Partners:\ndnata India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with dnata India South Asia Partners!",
